                     <interp inst="t18491126-102-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 1 hood and other articles, value 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18491126-name-615" type="victimName">
